# 🏦 TRACE: Transactional Risk Analysis & Compliance Engine

This submission contains a complete project skeleton and a full implementation of the three required modules under `starter/src/`.

## Structure
- `data/` sample CSVs (replace with official starter data if provided)
- `src/` implementation (`foundation_sar.py`, `risk_analyst_agent.py`, `compliance_officer_agent.py`)
- `notebooks/` completed notebooks for phases 1-4
- `outputs/` contains sample artifacts and audit logs

## Setup
1. Install dependencies:
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```
2. Copy and fill `.env`:
```bash
cp .env.template .env
```
3. Run notebooks in order (`01`, `02`, `03`).

## Testing
If your starter includes `tests/`, run:
```bash
python -m pytest tests/ -v
```

## Notes
The notebooks are written for Vocareum routing using `https://openai.vocareum.com/v1` as shown in the course guidance.
